org.imageterrier.dsms

Class AbstractRANSACGeomModifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.imageterrier.dsms.AbstractRANSACGeomModifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, org.terrier.matching.dsms.DocumentScoreModifier
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AffineScoreModifier, FundamentalScoreModifier, HomographyScoreModifier

    public abstract class AbstractRANSACGeomModifier
extends Object
implements org.terrier.matching.dsms.DocumentScoreModifier
    Abstract base class for DocumentScoreModifiers that use RANSAC to fit a geometric model to matching pairs of visual terms. Use of this class (or subclasses) requires that you are using a PositionInvertedIndex with a PositionSpec that has encoded spatial (x and y) coordinates for each term posting.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare
